                        <div class="collapse" id="collapse-3"style=" font-size: 12px">
                            <p class="text-justify" style="font-weight: normal;"><br>According to the terms of this Agreement, Tenant agrees to rent the Rental Property from Landlord for residential use, together with the following furnishings and/or appliances.  Rental of the premises also includes the following ancillary use. </p>
