                    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px"><a class="" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-4" role="button" href="#collapse-4">Term of tenancy <i class="fa fa-caret-down"></i></a>
                        <div class="collapse" id="collapse-4" style=" font-size: 12px">
                            <p class="text-justify" style="font-weight: normal;"><br>The term of rental will start on Moving in date and continue through the date decided by Landlord.  </p>
                        </div>
